  "title": "Operations Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise a group of carpark and enforcement staff.</li>\n  <li>Client relationships.</li>\n  <li>Project management.</li>\n  <li>Operations audit.</li>\n  <li>Prepare daily and monthly reports.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum “O” &amp; “N” Levels/ Equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 1-2 years of supervisory experience.</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Word and Excel.</li>\n  <li>Good leadership qualities.</li>\n  <li>Must possess own mode of transport (motorcycle/car).</li>\n</ul>",
